== Welcome to Sandler Control Panel for Infusionsoft

This application is designed to give you a quick and intuitive interface to the most important functions in your Infusionsoft application.

You can...

* add a new contact
* create events (briefings, bootcamps etc.)
* add contacts to an event
* remove contacts from an event
* view all contacts who are booked on to a particular event
* initiate a sales opportunity with a contact (book an appointment)
* convert a contact to a client
